* Following the disqualification of [[Andriy Kvyatkovskyi]] at the [[2016 European Wrestling Olympic Qualification Tournament|European Qualification Tournament]], his spot went to [[Zurabi Iakobishvili]] from Georgia. Following this adjustment, [[Borislav Novachkov]] earns the Olympic quota won by Georgia.<ref name="Doping">{{cite web|url=https://unitedworldwrestling.org/article/adjustments-to-olympic-qualifiers-announced|title=Adjustments to Olympic Qualifiers Announced|publisher=[[United World Wrestling]]|date=11 May 2016|accessdate=12 May 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805134918/https://unitedworldwrestling.org/article/adjustments-to-olympic-qualifiers-announced|archive-date=2016-08-05|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref>

