* Following the disqualification of [[Alen Zasyeyev]] at the [[2016 European Wrestling Olympic Qualification Tournament|European Qualification Tournament]] in Serbia, his spot went to [[Dániel Ligeti]] from Hungary. Following this adjustment, [[Aiaal Lazarev]] earns the Olympic quota won by Hungary. Bulgaria would have been the replacement but was also earned the quota in Serbia.<ref name="Doping" />

