{{Infobox Stadium | stadium_name = Bunamwaya Stadium | image = | location = [[Wakiso Town]], [[Uganda]] | coordinates = | broke_ground = | opened = | renovated = | closed = | demolished = | owner = | operator = | construction_cost = | architect = | former_names = | tenants = [[Bunamwaya SC]] | seating_capacity = 5,000 }}
'''Bunamwaya Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Wakiso Town]], [[Uganda]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and serves as the home venue of [[Bunamwaya SC]] of the [[Ugandan Super League]]. The stadium has a capacity of 5,000 people.<ref>http://www.worldstadiums.com/africa/countries/uganda.shtml</ref>
