{{Infobox country at games | NOC = JPN | NOCname = [[Japanese Olympic Committee]] | oldcode = | year = 1986 | date = | games = Asian Games | location = [[Seoul]] | competitors = | sports = | flagbearer = | officials = | gold = 58 | silver = 76 | bronze = 77 | rank = 3 | appearances = auto | seealso = | website = }}
'''[[Japan]]''' participated in the [[1986 Asian Games]] held in [[Seoul]], [[South Korea]] from September 20, 1986 to October 5, 1986. This country was ranked 3rd with 58 gold medals, 76 silver medals and 77 bronze medals with a total of 211 medals to secure its third spot in the medal tally.<ref>[http://www.ocasia.org/10AG.asp 1986 Asian Games medal tally] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307052031/http://www.ocasia.org/10AG.asp |date=2009-03-07 }}</ref>
