'''[[Mongolia]]''' competed at the '''[[1968 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Mexico City]], [[Mexico]]. 16 competitors, 12 men and 4 women, took part in 26 events in 4 sports.<ref name="SportsRef">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/MGL/summer/1968/ |title=Mongolia at the 1968 Mexico City Summer Games |accessdate=24 December 2015 |work=Sports Reference}}</ref>
