{{context|date=June 2013}} '''[[Møbelringen Cup]] 2009''' was held in [[Norway]], in the cities of [[Orkanger]] and [[Trondheim]]. The tournament started on 20 November and finished on 22 November 2009. [[Norway women's national handball team|Norway]] won the event by winning all their matches.
